sourcesContent: import React, { useState } from 'react'; import SideNav, { NavItem, NavIcon, NavText } from '@trendmicro/react-sidenav'; import '@trendmicro/react-sidenav/dist/react-sidenav.css'; import './SideBar.css' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router'; const SideBar = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [selected,setSelected] = useState('Sound') return ( { navigate('/'+selected) }} className = 'mysidebar'> SOUND CONFIGURATION DEVICE NETWORK PICTURE SOURCE CLOCK SYSTEM SYSTEM INFO ); }; export default SideBar;
